embeds.title: Spore
embeds.description:
Hey, I'm Jess and I'm just your average busy college student that likes to tinker.
I joined Discord in March 2017 because my friend and I decided skype was stupid and we needed a different platform to talk on. As I said above, I like to tinker and I am also a robotics and tech enthusiast. Unfortunately I end up breaking everything around me whether it's software or hardware.
I became a part of the Google Product Forums in 2016 and still try to help there as well as here on this Discord server when I get the chance. I love helping people with a passion, which is why I'm here! I'm also a moderator on r/ChromeOS.
In my freetime (If I get any) I like drawing, looking at Roombas to adopt, and playing various mobile games.
